APPROVAL NOTIFICATION Please do not reply to this message. If you need assistance or have questions, please contact your local representative

Dear Approver,


This mail is sent to you to notify Quote {!SBQQ__Quote__c.Name}  needs your approval :


- End Customer Company :{!SBQQ__Quote__c.NATT_End_Customer_Company__c}
- Account name : {!SBQQ__Quote__c.SBQQ__Account__c}
- Account owner : {!SBQQ__Quote__c.NATT_Account_Owner__c}
- Opportunity name : {!SBQQ__Quote__c.NATT_Opportunity_Name__c}
- Quote Number : {!SBQQ__Quote__c.Name}
- Opportunity Probability : {!SBQQ__Quote__c.NATT_Opportunity_Probability__c} %
- Amount : {!SBQQ__Quote__c.NATT_Opportunity_Amount__c}
- Quote average discount : {!SBQQ__Quote__c.SBQQ__AverageCustomerDiscount__c} %
- Max Discount: {!SBQQ__Quote__c.NATT_Max_Discount__c} %
- Quote Validity: {!SBQQ__Quote__c.SBQQ__ExpirationDate__c}
- Payment Terms: {!SBQQ__Quote__c.SBQQ__PaymentTerms__c}
- End Customer Payment Terms: {!SBQQ__Quote__c.Condiciones_de_Pago__c}
- End Customer Quotation Expiration Date: {!SBQQ__Quote__c.Vigencia_de_la_cotizaci_n__c}

Direct link to Opportunity: {!SBQQ__Quote__c.NATT_Opportunity_Link__c}

Direct link to Quote: {!SBQQ__Quote__c.Quote_Link__c}

Thank you!
